Logo and Brand Assets

**White-label partners receive:** high-resolution Provenarc Aero Solutions logo
files in multiple formats, brand color specifications (deep navy
#2E75B6, amber gold #D97706), typography guidelines, and co-branded
template options where both your brokerage logo and Provenarc Aero Solutions logo
appear together.

Customization Services

For white-label partners with established brand guidelines, Provenarc Aero Solutions
will customize all deliverable templates to match your visual identity.
This includes letterhead, folder structures, cover memos, and
client-facing communications. Turnaround time for template
customization: 5--7 business days after receipt of brand guidelines.

Getting Started: Three Simple Steps

1.  **Select Your Partnership Model**

Review the three models outlined in this document (Standard Referral
Commission, White-Label/Co-Branded, or Volume Partner with Tiered
Incentives). Determine which structure aligns with your business
objectives. If uncertain, schedule a consultation call with Provenarc Aero Solutions
to discuss your transaction volume, client demographics, and service
delivery preferences.

2.  **Execute Partnership Agreement**

Provenarc Aero Solutions will provide a standard partnership agreement covering
terms, pricing, SLA commitments, commission payment schedules (if
applicable), confidentiality, and termination provisions. Agreement
review and execution typically completes within 5--7 business days.
Legal review on your end is encouraged but not required.

3.  **Onboarding and Launch**

Provenarc Aero Solutions conducts a 60-minute onboarding session (in-person at your
office or via video conference) covering service capabilities, client
referral process, logistics coordination, white-label branding setup (if
applicable), and answers to your team\'s questions. You receive all
marketing materials and begin referring clients immediately. First job
typically processes within 7--14 days of partnership launch.

Frequently Asked Questions

**What is the minimum commitment required?**

There is no minimum job volume, no exclusivity requirement, and no
upfront fees. The partnership agreement is cancellable by either party
with 30 days written notice. You refer clients as opportunities arise.
If no referrals occur in a given month, there are no penalties or
obligations.

**How are commissions paid?**

For the standard referral commission model, payments are made within 30
days of job completion. Payment methods include ACH direct deposit,
check, or wire transfer. Monthly statements are provided showing all
completed jobs, gross revenue, commission owed, and payment date. No
minimum payout threshold applies.

**What happens if a client is dissatisfied?**

Provenarc Aero Solutions maintains a 100% satisfaction guarantee. If any aspect of
the service does not meet our quality standards or the client\'s
expectations, we will re-scan the affected materials at no charge. If
the issue cannot be resolved, a full refund is provided. For white-label
partners, client satisfaction issues are handled cooperatively to
preserve your client relationship while resolving the service concern.

**Can I offer digitization to buyers and sellers?**

Yes. The most common workflow is offering Transaction Ready packages to
sellers (as part of listing preparation) and Pre-Buy Inspection Support
to buyers (during due diligence). Both services drive value at different
stages of the transaction lifecycle and are complementary rather than
competitive.

**What geographic area does Provenarc Aero Solutions serve?**

Concierge pickup and return at no additional charge is provided within a
70-mile radius of Kerrville, Texas (Louis Schreiner Field / KERV). This
covers the Texas Hill Country including Boerne, Fredericksburg, New
Braunfels, and San Antonio. For aircraft located outside this radius,
Provenarc Aero Solutions can travel by car or by plane to provide white-glove
service nationwide. Extended travel fees apply for distances beyond 70
miles and are calculated based on actual travel time and mileage.

**What if logbooks are already partially digitized?**

Provenarc Aero Solutions can append new entries to existing digital files or perform
a complete re-scan if the prior digitization does not meet professional
standards (common with owner-performed smartphone scans). Pricing for
update services is lower than full digitization. The Subscription
Maintenance service (Tier 9) at \$29--\$49/month is specifically
designed for clients who want ongoing updates rather than one-time
conversion.

